text:
Hey everyone! Looks like most of you will be demoing tonight. I will have the rooms open if you want to be on zoom with your group while you wait. Just make sure you are paying attention to slack so when the TA invites you demo, you can be prepared.

Make sure you have your project up and running and ready to share your screen to show off your project.

Good luck everyone! Rooms will be open at 630 with the same breakout room setup if you choose to hang in the zoom rooms while you wait to be called to demo.
